ching, sprite/SVG mode switching, data attributes, and the overall icon wrapper"},"328":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-56","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#available-slot-overrides","content":"**`icon.content`**: Overrides the BentoIllustration component - affects SVG transformations (rotate, flip), accessibility attributes (`role`, `focusable`, `aria-labelledby`), viewBox calculations, and final SVG element rendering"},"329":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-57","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#available-slot-overrides","content":"For complete slot override patterns and examples, see the `@bento/slots` package documentation."},"330":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-58","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icons","content":"While the Icon component loads design system approved icons from the CDN by default, teams can introduce custom icons using the underlying Bento Icon system."},"331":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-59","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#adding-icons-synchronously","content":"Use the `set` method to add custom icons that are available immediately:"},"332":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-60","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#adding-icons-asynchronously","content":"Use the `ondemand` method to load custom icons from your own sources:"},"333":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-61","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"The following methods are exported from `@godaddy/antares` for custom icon management:"},"334":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-62","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`set(icons)`**: Synchronously add icons to the store"},"335":{"id":"/docs