nted-controller-25","page_id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/segmented-controller#overflow","content":"When the number of options exceeds the width of the container, the component automatically shows scroll buttons to let users navigate. Users can also scroll horizontally to navigate the options."},"767":{"id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller-26","page_id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/segmented-controller#rtl-direction","content":"The segmented controller follows the current **layout direction** (LTR or RTL). By default, that direction is detected automatically from the browser or system settings."},"768":{"id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller-27","page_id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/segmented-controller#disabled-states","content":"Disable the entire group with `isDisabled` on the container, or disable individual segments with `isDisabled` on specific items."},"769":{"id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller-28","page_id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/segmented-controller#data-attributes","content":"Components automatically add data attributes for styling different states:"},"770":{"id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller-29","page_id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/segmented-controller#data-attributes","content":"**SegmentedController Container:** `data-disabled`"},"771":{"id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller-30","page_id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/segmented-controller#data-attributes","content":"**SegmentedControllerItem:** `data-selected`, `data-hovered`, `data-pressed`, `data-focus-visible`, `data-disabled`"},"772":{"id":"/docs/components/segmented-controller-31","page_id":"/docs/components/s